channel.title: Alcyoneus Revolution - RS2HD 525 Server
channel.description:
[ul][center][color=teal][size=25pt][i]525 Alcyoneus[/i][/size] The main aim of this server is to create a stable, decent and enjoyable server, with both Player vs Player, Player vs NPC and Skilling properties. When i mean decent, I mean nice economy, no customs items, npcs, clients. Something to as close to RS2 as a private server needs to be. Base- 508 RS2HD Converted Since I’ve realised many servers are going more and more away from the RuneScape theme, they're making a full on player killing server, which are plain boring... I hope I stay with this project and produce something worthwhile. [size=15pt] Old Updates-[/size] Search for my official thread buried on the 7th or so page. [size=15pt]Skills- [/size]
